{
  "texts": [
    "This feature assesses the availability and the type of authentication mechanism.",
    "Access control is an essential feature in a system to manage the roles and responsibilities of users.",
    "SIEM systems also require multiple roles such as Manager, Senior Analyst, and Junior Analyst and they have different levels of access to various modules of a SIEM system while they perform the day-to-day operations.",
    "In this feature, we evaluate the type of access control mechanism in the SIEM solutions.",
    "Fault tolerance is an important requirement for all critical systems."
  ]
}